DOC.HEADLINE: THIEF MAY HAVE DIANA ' S RECORDS
DOC.TEXT: Princess Diana returned Sunday night from vacation in Spain to face the possibility that her confidential medical_records had been stolen and might become public . Police confirmed that files were stolen July 22 from the office of her therapist in London . The files are thought to contain intimate revelations of her physical and mental_health during the breakdown of her marriage to Prince Charles . They were contained in a small computer used by Roderick Lane , a clinical nutritionist who treated Diana during a reported struggle with bulimia .
